Package com.spectralogic.ds3client.helpers.pagination

This package contains many base implementations for supporting Spectra S3 calls that can be paginated.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PaginatingCommand<E,T extends AbstractPaginationRequest,F extends AbstractPaginationResponse>
    This interface is used to implement the call specific logic for any Spectra S3 paginated request.

    Class Description
    FileSystemKey

    GetBucketLoaderFactory
    This class is a child of GetBucketKeyLoaderFactory that provides a sane default for mapping ListBucketResult "/" will be used for the delimiter, and ListBucketResult will be mapped to LazyIterable.LazyLoader which was the old behavior.
    GetObjectsFullDetailsLoader  
    GetObjectsFullDetailsLoaderFactory
    A lazy implementation for paginating the Spectra S3 GetObjectsWithFullDetailsSpectraS3Request api call
    SpectraS3PaginationLoader<T,E extends AbstractPaginationRequest,F extends AbstractPaginationResponse>
    This class is used as the base implementation for all Spectra S3 paginating calls.
